name: Tobey Blomfield
title: President
bio: Hi, I'm Tobey. I'm in my second year of a Bachelor of Maths, majoring in pure mathematics. I love learning more maths, and I always like a nice proof or counter example. I'm also known for (and quite enjoy) pushing Desmos to it's limits.

name: Ben Varley
title: Secretary
bio: Hi, I'm Ben! I'm a fifth year Maths and Computer Science student with a focus on Applied Mathematics and Operations Research. I love cooking and playing board games with my free time.

name: Jasper Chong
title: Treasurer
bio: Hi I'm Jasper, a second year engineering and mathematics student with a focus on software and statistics. I really enjoy seeing all of the applications of mathematical modelling and prediction!

name: Max Orchard
title: Vice President
bio: Hi, I'm Max and I'm a first-year PhD student in mathematics. I enjoy softball, and also a little bit of hobby programming here and there. I don't enjoy when the vendo's cooling isn't working :(

name: Wolski
title: Industry Liaison
bio: Hi, I'm Wolski. I'm a 4th year maths and physics student with a particular focus on algebra, and a public love of Zorn's Lemma. In my off time, I like to cook, read, write music and play tabletop games of all varieties.
